  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F.",
    "Mix chicken with ginger paste, turmeric, black pepper, flour, cinnamon, olive oil, lemon juice, and zest in a large bowl.",
    "Season with salt and ensure the mixture is well coated on all sides.",
    "Transfer the seasoned chicken into a bamboo tray and bake for 30 minutes.",
    "Remove from oven and let it rest for about 10 minutes before serving.",
    "Optional: Garnish with fresh cilantro or mint leaves."
